    log /dev/log local0
    log /dev/log local1 notice

    maxconn 4000
    user haproxy
    group haproxy
    daemon

    mode    http
    option  httplog
    option  dontlognull
    retries 3
    option  redispatch
    option  http-server-close
    option  forwardfor except 127.0.0.0/8
    timeout connect 5000ms
    timeout client  50000ms
    timeout server  50000ms
